Installation Instructions
-------------------------


Dependencies (the Ubuntu package names are used)
-----------------------

qt4-dev (must have qt version 4.4 or greater)
libsqlite3-dev
libsoci-core-gcc
libsoci-core-gcc-dev
libsoci-sqlite3-gcc
cmake (this is the build system used, verion 2.6 or greater)
libginac-dev
libgsl0-dev (version 1.9 or greater)
libboost-dev C++ libraries 

Build and run instructions
----------------------------

1. run cmake
2. run make
3. execute ark3d


Example build and run process
------------------------------------

cmake .
make
./src/Interface/ark3d



